    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-osel",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given established regulatory precedent for single-configuration F1717 submissions and the strong multi-site experimental dataset. The validation metric E/uval falls below 1.96 for all three QoIs, and the sensitivity analysis confirms robustness of predictions to plausible input uncertainty. The FEA modelling framework is assessed as sufficiently credible for submission support within the defined COU.",
